isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italy-seizes-chinese-made-military-drones-destined-libya-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>智库称，美国军事基地附近的新古巴雷达站可能有助于中国间谍活动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/new-cuban-radar-site-near-us-military-base-could-aid-china-spying-think-tank-2024-07-02/</link><description>古巴正在建设一个新的雷达站，可能能够监视美国附近的​​关塔那摩湾海军基地，这是华盛顿智库利用卫星图像发现的，这是该国监视能力的最新升级，长期以来一直被认为与中国有关。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 16:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/new-cuban-radar-site-near-us-military-base-could-aid-china-spying-think-tank-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，柏林将阻止曼恩能源解决方案公司的燃气轮机部门向中国出售</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/berlin-block-sale-man-energy-solutions-gas-turbine-unit-china-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>三名知情人士周二告诉路透社，德国将阻止大众汽车子公司曼能源解决方案公司燃气轮机部门向一家中国公司出售的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 15:45:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/berlin-block-sale-man-energy-solutions-gas-turbine-unit-china-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>国土安全部称美国包机驱逐中国移民</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-deported-chinese-migrants-charter-flight-homeland-security-says-2024-07-02/</link><description>美国国土安全部周二表示，美国在周末将试图非法入境的中国人驱逐回中国，这是自 2018 年以来的首次大型包机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 14:22:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-deported-chinese-migrants-charter-flight-homeland-security-says-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>美国将六家公司列入贸易限制名单，其中四家用于培训中国军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-adds-six-companies-trade-restriction-list-four-training-chinas-military-2024-07-02/</link><description>据政府公告称，美国周二将六家公司列入贸易限制名单，其中四家因与中国军队训练有联系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:23:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-adds-six-companies-trade-restriction-list-four-training-chinas-military-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>文件显示拜登2024年吊销了中国华为的8张许可证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</link><description>据路透社最先报道的一份文件显示，拜登政府今年吊销了八项允许一些公司向中国电信设备巨头华为运送货物的许可证，试图向这家复兴的公司施压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪与法国艾文斯建立欧洲合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</link><description>法国兴业银行的汽车租赁部门艾文斯与中国电动汽车公司比亚迪周二宣布建立欧洲市场合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，京东是英国包裹公司 Evri 的可能竞购者之一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/jdcom-among-possible-bidders-british-parcel-company-evri-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国在线零售商京东已成为几家正在考虑竞购英国包裹递送公司 Evri 的公司之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/jdcom-among-possible-bidders-british-parcel-company-evri-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾将“坚持不懈”保护南海利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</link><description>菲律宾和中国周二一致认为，需要“恢复信任”和“重建信心”，以更好地管理海上争端，尽管马尼拉告诉其邻国，它将“毫不留情”地保护其在南海的利益。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>被控为中国从事间谍活动的挪威男子出庭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</link><description>一名警方官员表示，一名挪威男子周二在奥斯陆法院出庭，面临代表中国从事间谍活动的指控，最初将被拘留四个星期，这是涉及中国在欧洲从事间谍活动的最新案件。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉 6 月中国制造电动汽车销量同比下降 24.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二的数据显示，特斯拉6月份中国制造的电动汽车销量同比下降24.2%至71,007辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国和澳大利亚在太平洋影响力竞赛中捐赠建筑物和机场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国在瓦努阿图捐赠了一座总统大楼，澳大利亚和新西兰则在邻国所罗门群岛斥资 5500 万澳元落成机场，以争夺在太平洋岛屿地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>